  <ThingDef ParentName="ApparelArmorPowerTenebralBase">
    <defName>BOR_Tenebral_Apparel_PowerArmor</defName>
    <label>tenebral marine armor</label>
    <description>A suit of tenebral powered armor. Layered tenebrite-weave plates are very effective at stopping attacks, with few vulnerable joint sections. Neuro-memetic assistors allow a human to wear the armor and still move easily.\n\nArmor like this is often used by rapid-incursion space marines.</description>
